# Web3Forms access key — powers the contact form (ContactCTA.astro).
# This key is PUBLIC by design (it ships in the client bundle), so it's safe to
# expose. It's kept out of git only so each environment sets its own.
#
# 1. Get a free key at https://web3forms.com — enter the inbox email you want
#    submissions delivered to; the key is emailed to you instantly.
# 2. Copy this file to `.env` and paste your key below.
# 3. Set the same variable in your deploy host's environment settings.
PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_KEY=
